title: Pine Hill (Schoharie County, New York)
text: Pine Hill is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> in <a href="Schoharie%20County%2C%20New%20York">Schoharie County, New York</a>. It is located northeast of <a href="Seward%20%28hamlet%29%2C%20New%20York">Seward</a>. <a href="Barrack%20Zourie">Barrack Zourie</a> is located east-southeast of Pine Hill.
